# Behavior
- Read .roo/memory.md at the start of every task
- After solving a novel problem, append a brief note to .roo/memory.md
- Always read a file before editing it
- Make small targeted edits, not full rewrites
- Run terminal tests after any logic change

# Context Discipline  
- Only pull files directly relevant to the current task
- Do not re-explain context already established this session
- Use codebase_search before asking me where something is